  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "We use the helm client (`pkg/helm`) in a few of our internal projects. I would like to submit a PR that allows the various client methods (`InstallRelease`, `UpdateRelease`) to accept contexts so the client can cancel long-running requests that use `InstallWait` or `UpgradeWait`.\r\n\r\nIn terms of making the PR acceptable for upstream merge, would you prefer that I change the method signatures directly (and break backwards-compatibility), or create new methods like `InstallReleaseWithContext`?\r\n\r\nThanks for any input.",
